snippet.title: Sulfur - Official Xbox Reveal Trailer | ID@Xbox April 2024
snippet.description: Blast through enemies and see a variety of gear in this latest action-packed trailer for Sulfur, an upcoming modern old-school action-adventure game. Sulfur is coming to Xbox and PC. In Sulfur, outsmart enemies, find treasure, improve weapons, harness powers. Delve deeper, find answers, make it end.
